Short description: Baro sida ilmaha loo baro inuu is-dabiro

Description: Koorsadan waxaad ku baranaysaa sida loo kobciyo caqliga ilmahaaga.

Name: Koorsada Ilmaha Hadalka ka soo Daaho

Name: Koorsada Badqabka Qoyska iyo Xalinta Khilaafka
